1
00:00:05,090 --> 00:00:06,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yelenetta's attacking!</font>

2
00:00:06,990 --> 00:00:08,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Evacuate!</font>

3
00:00:09,900 --> 00:00:11,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't believe it.</font>

4
00:00:15,020 --> 00:00:17,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Arte's homeland...</font>

5
00:00:21,630 --> 00:00:23,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No way.</font>

6
00:00:30,040 --> 00:00:32,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-Mother!</font>

7
00:00:45,370 --> 00:00:50,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EASYGOING TERRITORY DEFENSE
BY THE OPTIMISTIC LORD</font>

8
00:00:50,520 --> 00:00:53,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 12: EASYGOING TERRITORY
DEFENSE BY THE OPTIMISTIC LORD</font>

9
00:02:05,990 --> 00:02:14,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 12: EASYGOING TERRITORY
DEFENSE BY THE OPTIMISTIC LORD</font>

10
00:02:06,260 --> 00:02:13,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}In short, their commander says Yelenetta
Kingdom's plan was a three-pronged attack.</font>

11
00:02:14,660 --> 00:02:18,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seatoh and Scudet 
were two of those prongs.</font>

12
00:02:19,020 --> 00:02:21,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the last one is...</font>

13
00:02:22,390 --> 00:02:24,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ferdinatto County.</font>

14
00:02:29,250 --> 00:02:30,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Arte's homeland.</font>

15
00:02:33,780 --> 00:02:34,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Van.</font>

16
00:02:36,580 --> 00:02:39,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please let me go there.</font>

17
00:02:39,740 --> 00:02:41,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, I'll go, too.</font>

18
00:02:41,370 --> 00:02:42,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

19
00:02:43,470 --> 00:02:46,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't rely on you 
for everything, Lord Van.</font>

20
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:49,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you're talking about 
going off to war.</font>

21
00:02:51,430 --> 00:02:53,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is a family matter.</font>

22
00:02:55,230 --> 00:02:58,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've never seen Arte 
this stubborn before.</i></font>

23
00:03:07,430 --> 00:03:09,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

24
00:03:10,570 --> 00:03:15,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you're genuinely worried
 about me, Lord Van. But I...</font>

25
00:03:16,820 --> 00:03:22,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I see. If I were to save 
Ferdinatto County from danger...</font>

26
00:03:23,310 --> 00:03:26,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the lord of 
a small, remote village.</font>

27
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:29,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If someone like you saved them...</font>

28
00:03:29,260 --> 00:03:32,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mm-hmm. Count Ferdinatto
 would lose his standing</font>

29
00:03:32,860 --> 00:03:35,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and maybe even his land as well.</font>

30
00:03:37,270 --> 00:03:43,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess that's all there is to say. But can
 I at least provide you with an escort?</font>

31
00:03:43,610 --> 00:03:47,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. Thank you for your consideration.</font>

32
00:03:47,590 --> 00:03:50,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please leave that to us.</font>

33
00:03:50,520 --> 00:03:54,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She'll definitely be safe 
with us guarding her.</font>

34
00:03:54,260 --> 00:03:57,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll protect your future wife.</font>

35
00:03:58,410 --> 00:04:02,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ortho? And you, too, Kusala and Pluriel?</font>

36
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:06,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine. We just want 
to help you out, Lord Van.</font>

37
00:04:06,070 --> 00:04:11,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, adventurers like us getting 
involved won't create any issues.</font>

38
00:04:13,860 --> 00:04:17,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. Please take care
 of Arte, you guys.</font>

39
00:04:27,570 --> 00:04:30,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-Mother!</font>

40
00:04:31,850 --> 00:04:33,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, young lady!</font>

41
00:04:40,050 --> 00:04:42,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Drop the black balls!</font>

42
00:04:52,740 --> 00:04:53,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Arte.</font>

43
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:57,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we join the battle now, 
we might be able to turn the tide.</font>

44
00:04:57,990 --> 00:05:00,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please let me command this squad.</font>

45
00:05:06,620 --> 00:05:08,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't.</font>

46
00:05:08,450 --> 00:05:13,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It must be someone from House Ferdinatto
who drives out Yelenetta Kingdom.</font>

47
00:05:13,770 --> 00:05:16,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But how will you handle that army?</font>

48
00:05:22,210 --> 00:05:24,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry and evacuate!</font>

49
00:05:24,260 --> 00:05:25,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Save me!</font>

50
00:05:26,930 --> 00:05:28,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How can this be?</font>

51
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe Yelenetta's army
 is attacking us.</font>

52
00:05:34,230 --> 00:05:36,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-Mother.</font>

53
00:05:37,950 --> 00:05:39,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must not cry.</font>

54
00:05:40,460 --> 00:05:45,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}SHARON TORA FERDINATTO</font>

55
00:05:40,590 --> 00:05:45,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'll make sure it looks like you 
committed suicide at the very end.</font>

56
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:49,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Later generations must see 
the eldest daughter ended her life cleanly</font>

57
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:50,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">like a noble should.</font>

58
00:05:52,590 --> 00:05:53,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't fret.</font>

59
00:05:57,140 --> 00:05:58,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mother.</font>

60
00:05:59,900 --> 00:06:01,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Mother.</i></font>

61
00:06:03,060 --> 00:06:03,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Arte?</font>

62
00:06:05,940 --> 00:06:10,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ferdinatto County is no match 
for the Yelenetta army.</font>

63
00:06:11,400 --> 00:06:13,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, let's conquer it!</font>

64
00:06:13,640 --> 00:06:15,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

65
00:06:19,370 --> 00:06:22,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Victory is already ours.</font>

66
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:32,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What just happened?</font>

67
00:06:32,180 --> 00:06:35,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A silver knight is attacking the wyverns!</font>

68
00:06:36,030 --> 00:06:37,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A silver knight?</font>

69
00:06:58,210 --> 00:07:00,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-That's impossible.</font>

70
00:07:00,480 --> 00:07:03,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They took out <i>all </i>of 
those wyverns in a flash!</font>

71
00:07:04,250 --> 00:07:05,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell <i>is</i> that thing?</font>

72
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:08,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Commander, this is bad!</font>

73
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:11,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">House Ferdinatto's flag 
has been spotted on the hill!</font>

74
00:07:15,830 --> 00:07:20,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it. Curse the Scuderian army. 
They sent reinforcements, huh?</font>

75
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:22,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Change target to the forces on the hill.</font>

76
00:07:22,860 --> 00:07:24,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll attack with our full might!</font>

77
00:07:25,090 --> 00:07:27,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what about the silver knight?</font>

78
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:30,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Won't be worth fearing 
if we crush their main force.</font>

79
00:07:30,830 --> 00:07:33,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, go annihilate them!</font>

80
00:07:33,180 --> 00:07:36,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

81
00:07:37,110 --> 00:07:41,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The enemy's coming to crush us first.</font>

82
00:07:41,780 --> 00:07:45,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I knew it wouldn't go as easily 
as it did for Lord Van.</i></font>

83
00:07:45,140 --> 00:07:47,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't know enough about battle.</i></font>

84
00:07:48,100 --> 00:07:50,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And I can't stop my hands from shaking.</i></font>

85
00:07:53,700 --> 00:07:57,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I have to do all I can.</i></font>

86
00:07:59,700 --> 00:08:00,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ortho.</font>

87
00:08:01,670 --> 00:08:02,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

88
00:08:03,390 --> 00:08:07,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, but could I
 ask you for support?</font>

89
00:08:07,800 --> 00:08:10,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, of course.</font>

90
00:08:11,660 --> 00:08:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone...</font>

91
00:08:13,790 --> 00:08:16,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please lend me your strength.</font>

92
00:08:16,670 --> 00:08:20,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please help me save my homeland.</font>

93
00:08:24,060 --> 00:08:24,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone...</font>

94
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:27,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please lend me your strength.</font>

95
00:08:27,830 --> 00:08:31,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please help me save my homeland.</font>

96
00:08:33,350 --> 00:08:36,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you planning to do, Lady Arte?</font>

97
00:08:37,060 --> 00:08:38,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm...</font>

98
00:08:41,090 --> 00:08:42,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to the front line.</font>

99
00:08:43,800 --> 00:08:44,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Arte?</font>

100
00:08:45,690 --> 00:08:47,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Automaton! Uno!</font>

101
00:08:49,650 --> 00:08:51,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get them!</font>

102
00:08:57,670 --> 00:09:01,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it. How are they 
so overwhelmingly strong?</font>

103
00:09:03,350 --> 00:09:05,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. We're going, too.</font>

104
00:09:05,020 --> 00:09:07,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

105
00:09:15,650 --> 00:09:17,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Settle down!</font>

106
00:09:18,650 --> 00:09:20,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? I can't move!</font>

107
00:09:21,770 --> 00:09:23,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like it's my turn.</font>

108
00:09:26,380 --> 00:09:28,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Piece of cake.</font>

109
00:09:28,260 --> 00:09:31,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How dare you hurt my brother-in-arms!</font>

110
00:09:32,890 --> 00:09:33,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kusala!</font>

111
00:09:35,050 --> 00:09:37,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Prepare yourself!</font>

112
00:09:42,970 --> 00:09:43,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Its arm...</font>

113
00:09:47,170 --> 00:09:49,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? You can still move?</font>

114
00:09:51,260 --> 00:09:51,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

115
00:09:57,430 --> 00:09:59,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You saved me there.</font>

116
00:09:59,760 --> 00:10:02,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Lady Arte.</font>

117
00:10:33,090 --> 00:10:34,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good.</font>

118
00:10:34,620 --> 00:10:37,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like we've taken 
control of this area.</font>

119
00:10:37,470 --> 00:10:41,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it finally over?
 We had quite a tough time of it.</font>

120
00:10:41,740 --> 00:10:42,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not yet!</font>

121
00:10:48,590 --> 00:10:49,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

122
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:52,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way.</font>

123
00:10:52,750 --> 00:10:54,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They have <i>that</i> many wyverns?</font>

124
00:10:54,780 --> 00:10:57,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's roughly 50 of them.</font>

125
00:10:58,650 --> 00:11:02,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It always pays to be cautious. 
I requested reinforcements.</font>

126
00:11:03,300 --> 00:11:05,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, wyverns!</font>

127
00:11:05,310 --> 00:11:08,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take down that silver knight!</font>

128
00:11:09,770 --> 00:11:11,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! We're in trouble!</font>

129
00:11:17,370 --> 00:11:18,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look out!</font>

130
00:11:23,050 --> 00:11:24,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-That's...</font>

131
00:11:24,860 --> 00:11:27,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Another of Lady Arte's marionettes?</font>

132
00:11:28,630 --> 00:11:32,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way... She can move two at once?</font>

133
00:11:35,670 --> 00:11:38,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My mana won't last long like this.</font>

134
00:11:40,140 --> 00:11:42,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep the pressure on!</font>

135
00:11:46,680 --> 00:11:49,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's just too many of them.</font>

136
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:54,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Decimate our enemies...</font>

137
00:11:55,550 --> 00:11:57,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aventador!</font>

138
00:12:05,290 --> 00:12:09,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've always believed I was a failure.</i></font>

139
00:12:11,330 --> 00:12:13,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even though I was a noble,</i></font>

140
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:15,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>my aptitude was for marionette magic.</i></font>

141
00:12:22,010 --> 00:12:25,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A type of magic loathed by all.</i></font>

142
00:12:26,070 --> 00:12:28,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I swore I would never use it
 in front of others again.</i></font>

143
00:12:32,810 --> 00:12:36,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But then, Lord Van saved me.</i></font>

144
00:12:40,460 --> 00:12:42,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Because I met Lord Van,</i></font>

145
00:12:42,860 --> 00:12:45,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was able to gain confidence.</i></font>

146
00:12:53,550 --> 00:12:55,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What power...</font>

147
00:12:55,700 --> 00:12:58,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She took out more than half 
in the blink of an eye.</font>

148
00:12:58,950 --> 00:13:00,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Incredible.</font>

149
00:13:02,010 --> 00:13:03,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you <i>doing</i>?</font>

150
00:13:03,920 --> 00:13:06,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Crush them!</font>

151
00:13:12,670 --> 00:13:13,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I...</i></font>

152
00:13:19,650 --> 00:13:24,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I will save those precious to me
 with this magic!</i></font>

153
00:13:32,260 --> 00:13:34,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Last one!</i></font>

154
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:44,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-That's impossible.</font>

155
00:13:44,830 --> 00:13:47,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yelenetta's army...</font>

156
00:13:48,370 --> 00:13:49,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm getting outta here!</font>

157
00:13:49,800 --> 00:13:50,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're too strong!</font>

158
00:13:50,930 --> 00:13:52,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't win!</font>

159
00:13:53,660 --> 00:13:54,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We did it!</font>

160
00:13:54,980 --> 00:13:57,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We won!</font>

161
00:13:57,100 --> 00:13:59,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

162
00:13:59,720 --> 00:14:01,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We did it!</font>

163
00:14:12,770 --> 00:14:17,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were able to win thanks 
to these girls Lord Van gave me.</font>

164
00:14:20,180 --> 00:14:23,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry for making you fight 
until you got so battered.</font>

165
00:14:25,560 --> 00:14:29,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm truly grateful to you 
for saving my home.</font>

166
00:14:36,980 --> 00:14:40,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who in the world saved us?</font>

167
00:14:42,050 --> 00:14:44,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is where you were.</font>

168
00:14:45,810 --> 00:14:46,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Darling.</font>

169
00:14:47,270 --> 00:14:49,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry I was late.</font>

170
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:50,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad you're safe.</font>

171
00:14:51,220 --> 00:14:52,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Father.</font>

172
00:14:52,740 --> 00:14:55,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you know anything 
about those reinforcements?</font>

173
00:14:56,260 --> 00:14:57,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

174
00:14:57,810 --> 00:15:04,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All I know now is that the Yelenetta army 
was driven off by just two marionettes.</font>

175
00:15:04,130 --> 00:15:05,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

176
00:15:06,060 --> 00:15:10,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The other thing I know is a young girl
 with white hair was standing at the head,</font>

177
00:15:10,520 --> 00:15:14,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">commanding those reinforcements.</font>

178
00:15:14,500 --> 00:15:15,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't mean...</font>

179
00:15:15,920 --> 00:15:17,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

180
00:15:17,950 --> 00:15:20,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No... It can't be!</font>

181
00:15:21,870 --> 00:15:23,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How ironic.</font>

182
00:15:24,420 --> 00:15:27,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Especially after we drove her
 from our home.</font>

183
00:15:29,930 --> 00:15:33,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We treated that girl poorly.</font>

184
00:15:46,820 --> 00:15:51,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure you aren't going home?
 Your parents are right there.</font>

185
00:15:51,820 --> 00:15:55,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would only cause them trouble
 if I went home.</font>

186
00:15:56,210 --> 00:16:00,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the city was saved 
thanks to your marionettes.</font>

187
00:16:00,560 --> 00:16:05,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The people will be overjoyed when they 
hear you were the one controlling them.</font>

188
00:16:05,210 --> 00:16:06,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even your parents—</font>

189
00:16:06,360 --> 00:16:07,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't be so sure.</font>

190
00:16:09,560 --> 00:16:14,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My mother loathed 
my marionette magic.</font>

191
00:16:16,210 --> 00:16:19,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go home. Lord Van is waiting for us.</font>

192
00:16:29,390 --> 00:16:32,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Arte has returned!</font>

193
00:16:35,670 --> 00:16:37,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Arte, are you hurt?</font>

194
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:42,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the matter?</font>

195
00:16:43,730 --> 00:16:45,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm no good.</font>

196
00:16:46,230 --> 00:16:48,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do you think that?</font>

197
00:16:48,810 --> 00:16:50,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

198
00:16:50,870 --> 00:16:56,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't issue commands to everyone 
with confidence like you do.</font>

199
00:16:57,110 --> 00:17:00,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think you're doing just fine.</font>

200
00:17:03,030 --> 00:17:06,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If anything, I can't understand why
 you're lacking confidence.</font>

201
00:17:06,970 --> 00:17:11,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, it's incredible how you move
 your marionettes so freely.</font>

202
00:17:12,390 --> 00:17:13,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

203
00:17:13,590 --> 00:17:15,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Panamera said it before.</font>

204
00:17:16,570 --> 00:17:21,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She hardly recognized you as the girl
 she brought here from that county.</font>

205
00:17:21,700 --> 00:17:25,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's because you're very kind, Lord Van.</font>

206
00:17:29,370 --> 00:17:30,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Arte.</font>

207
00:17:33,890 --> 00:17:35,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did very well.</font>

208
00:17:55,650 --> 00:17:56,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Arte.</font>

209
00:17:59,000 --> 00:17:59,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome home.</font>

210
00:18:06,600 --> 00:18:07,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm home.</font>

211
00:18:20,910 --> 00:18:25,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TRANSLATION: JOHN PICKETT</font>

212
00:18:25,170 --> 00:18:29,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TIMING: ANDY ELLIS
EDITING: SMR</font>

213
00:18:29,420 --> 00:18:33,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}QUALITY CONTROL: RILEY DALTON
TRANSLATION CHECK: REI MIYASAKA</font>

214
00:19:48,920 --> 00:19:49,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ta-da!</font>

215
00:19:49,940 --> 00:19:54,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've created new shops and 
a new inn in the center of town.</font>

216
00:19:55,470 --> 00:19:57,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, they're lovely.</font>

217
00:19:57,950 --> 00:20:02,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup. I want all of the villagers 
to enjoy a pleasant life, after all.</font>

218
00:20:06,210 --> 00:20:11,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was honestly worried about living here
 when I first arrived, but...</i></font>

219
00:20:13,260 --> 00:20:15,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you believe it?</font>

220
00:20:15,490 --> 00:20:19,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This once-impoverished place has 
transformed into such a lovely village.</font>

221
00:20:20,220 --> 00:20:21,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome!</font>

222
00:20:21,700 --> 00:20:23,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome to all.</font>

223
00:20:23,780 --> 00:20:27,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have the latest goods 
from the royal capital!</font>

224
00:20:27,290 --> 00:20:30,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please stop in and take a look.</font>

225
00:20:32,540 --> 00:20:35,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't go fallin' off now, grannies!</font>

226
00:20:41,020 --> 00:20:42,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see they haven't changed.</font>

227
00:20:44,040 --> 00:20:49,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We have all ages, races, 
and personality types in this village,</i></font>

228
00:20:52,310 --> 00:20:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but everyone gets along oddly well,
and they're all having fun.</i></font>

229
00:20:58,370 --> 00:21:00,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cheers!</font>

230
00:21:08,780 --> 00:21:11,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This meat is really good!</font>

231
00:21:11,850 --> 00:21:15,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Kusala! That was my meat!</font>

232
00:21:16,970 --> 00:21:19,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's your fifteenth drink.</font>

233
00:21:19,080 --> 00:21:20,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impressive, Lady Panamera.</font>

234
00:21:22,950 --> 00:21:24,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was born a noble,</i></font>

235
00:21:24,970 --> 00:21:30,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but my aptitude for production magic 
got me kicked out of my home by my father,</i></font>

236
00:21:30,140 --> 00:21:32,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and I became the lord
 of a remote village.</i></font>

237
00:21:33,650 --> 00:21:37,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>However, thanks to him, 
I've met many entertaining friends,</i></font>

238
00:21:37,450 --> 00:21:39,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and I was able to develop
 this remote village.</i></font>

239
00:21:42,480 --> 00:21:46,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I thought I'd lost my home, 
but I found myself enjoying life,</i></font>

240
00:21:46,610 --> 00:21:50,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and this village became precious
 to me before I knew it.</i></font>

241
00:21:55,230 --> 00:21:57,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, everyone.</font>

242
00:21:58,260 --> 00:21:59,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Van.</font>

243
00:22:00,750 --> 00:22:03,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is nearly time for your studies.</font>

244
00:22:04,090 --> 00:22:07,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll ensure you get a thorough education.</font>

245
00:22:08,380 --> 00:22:09,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Van!</font>

246
00:22:10,580 --> 00:22:13,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the era of swordsmanship!</font>

247
00:22:13,530 --> 00:22:18,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to train you to become 
this kingdom's greatest swordsman!</font>

248
00:22:18,810 --> 00:22:23,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, Lord Van shall become 
the kingdom's most astounding scholar.</font>

249
00:22:23,290 --> 00:22:25,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't let that stand.</font>

250
00:22:27,250 --> 00:22:29,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to be either!</font>

251
00:22:30,020 --> 00:22:31,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, hey, Lord Van!</font>

252
00:22:31,950 --> 00:22:33,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait up!</font>

253
00:22:35,610 --> 00:22:37,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so lively, isn't it?</font>

254
00:22:37,560 --> 00:22:40,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can do it, Lord Van!</font>

255
00:22:40,620 --> 00:22:43,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to run faster 
or they'll catch you.</font>

256
00:22:44,840 --> 00:22:46,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just a little further.</font>

257
00:22:47,080 --> 00:22:50,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's it! Go on!</font>

258
00:22:50,820 --> 00:22:54,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Run faster, young man!</font>

259
00:22:54,460 --> 00:22:57,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hang in there, Lord Van!</font>

260
00:23:30,810 --> 00:23:36,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay! I'm gonna continue making leisurely 
progress toward a fun place for all of us to live!</font>

